news.title: China's new home prices fall for fifth straight month in November 2023
news.para: New home prices fell 0.3% month-on-month, matching the figure in October, according to Reuters calculations based on National Bureau of Statistics (NBS) data.

news.title: China Evergrande to exit Shanghai Henggen Real Estate amid liquidity crunch
news.para: Shanghai Henggen was developing the Shanghai North Bund Project, which has generated no rental income during 2021 and 2022.

news.title: USA: Lennar Corp beats quarterly revenue on steady demand
news.para: Looking to the next year, the country's second-largest homebuilder said production time to build a home was normalizing as its supply chain and the labor market improved. Production, or cycle, time in the fourth quarter fell 24% year over year.

news.title: Chhattisgarh government clears 18 lakh PMAY houses
news.para: ​The cabinet met here at Mantralaya in the afternoon, a day after Sai took oath as the chief minister. Deputy CMs Arun Sao and Vijay Sharma, who too were sworn in on Wednesday, were present in the meeting.

news.title: CG Power and Industrial Solutions & K Raheja Corp to jointly develop Mumbai property
news.para: K Raheja Corp. will be granted development rights by CG Power and Industrial Solutions to develop the land admeasuring 4,262.34 sq meters by demolishing the existing structure.

news.title: Space hunting for slum rehabilitation to become easier in Pune
news.para: According to the new guidelines, slums can now be rehabilitated within 5 km from the periphery of the slum. According to the old guidelines, it was restricted to within 2 km only.

news.title: Hotel plots in Ayodhya fetch premium of 180%
news.para: The UP Housing Board earned a significant premium while auctioning the plots earmarked for hotels in the township. The response shows the pent-up demand from the private sector for freehold plots which are free from any kind of legal encumbrance.

news.title: Kalyan-Dombivli civic body seal five flats of developer over non payment of open lax tax dues
news.para: The action was taken by KDMC's Tax department. The KDMC sources said that the Wadhwa developer owns land in Barave area in Kalyan and for the last few years he has not paid open land tax despite several reminders sent by the tax department.

news.title: Mumbai: MMRDA to redevelop Ramabai slum to extend Freeway
news.para: A part of the extended alignment will pass through Ramabai Ambedkar Nagar for which MMRDA will have to acquire the slum land.

news.title: Finally, Chandigarh mayor forms house tax committee
news.para: ​This step of the Chandigarh Mayor seems to be taken to save his face from the criticism, as since January 2023, the month mayor assumed the charge, not even a single sub-committee of the MC was constituted.

news.title: Dosti Realty forays into redevelopment, plans Rs 1,000 crore investment to build portfolio
news.para: As its maiden project involving redevelopment work, the company has secured rights to redevelop a large housing society spread over a prime 2.5-acre land parcel in Thane’s Louis Wadi locality.

news.title: Conciliation bench a must to resolve complaints quickly: Haryana RERA chairman
news.para: “For this, a conciliation bench should be set up to resolve complaints at an early stage, which would help both parties — the allottees as well as the developer,” said Arun Kumar, Chairman, Haryana RERA (Gurugram bench)on Thursday.

news.title: Government rolls back three-tier property guideline value in Chennai
news.para: As per the three-tier guideline value, each neighbourhood would have a uniform guideline value for three categories of apartment complexes – basic, premium and ultra-premium – based on amenities.

news.title: German-based aluplast GmbH looks to invest €4 million in India in next two years
news.para: aluplast GmbH is expecting 50 per cent growth in its manufacturing capacity in India in the next two years and targeting that aluplast India contributes about 4-5 per cent of the overall volume of the company globally in 4-5 years time.

news.title: Haryana CM announces regularisation of 210 unauthorised colonies
news.para: The move is aimed at ensuring the provision of essential urban development and amenities for residents residing in these colonies as basic amenities such as roads, sewerage, water supply, and streetlights will be provided to them, Khattar said.

news.title: Country Garden sells stake in Dalian Wanda unit for $428 million
news.para: The sale of its 1.79% holding in shopping mall operator Zhuhai Wanda Commercial Management to Dalian Wanda Commercial Management Group helped shares in Country Garden climb 3% in Thursday trade.

news.title: State capital region to be notified soon in Uttar Pradesh
news.para: A total of 12 objections were submitted by various stakeholders by November 30 to the housing department for perusal which have been disposed of after the public hearing.

news.title: China's Beijing, Shanghai loosen home buying restrictions to aid housing market
news.para: The world's second-biggest economy has struggled to get back on its feet this year after reopening from COVID curbs, largely because its massive property sector has stumbled from one crisis to another in a major blow to consumer and investor confidence.
